data.description: *THIS WEEKEND - Seller to Offer $8,000 closing cost credit and include ALL Appliances. **Open House Sunday from 1pm to 3pm.*Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and location in this beautiful, corner unit, 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhome. Nestled in a picturesque and desirable, tree-lined neighborhood, this home offers a serene retreat while being conveniently close to all the amenities you desire. Beautifully updated bathrooms with quality finishes and modern touches. Kitchen with a large pantry and new fs-range w/ double ovens. Loft space can be used as an office or media area. -HOA includes High-speed Internet, Pool, Gym/weight-room, Community area. New roof coming soon.-Low maintenance home with added benefits of a great community.-Please allow for at least 2 hours notice for all showings. -Sellers current mortgage can potentially be transferred to new buyer with potential to save $$ with the existing rate. Ask for details. [Home Energy Score = 6. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222631]
